author: Jane Doe
testimonial: Jaroslav was a great teammate on our art gallery website project. He helped build layouts and components from Figma designs and consistently delivered clean, well-structured code. He’s reliable, quick to learn, and easy to collaborate with.

author: Jack Foe
testimonial: I had the pleasure of working with Jaroslav on the development of a website for an art gallery. He was responsible for creating several layouts and reusable components based on the provided designs. His work was well-structured, clean, and easy to integrate into the project. He showed a good eye for detail, communicated clearly, and was always open to feedback, which made collaboration smooth and efficient. His contribution played an important role in delivering a visually consistent and functional final website.
